      "Today I’m excited to announce Unify for Sales Reps, the biggest product launch in Unify’s 897 day history 🚀\n\nUnify already helps Growth teams at companies like Perplexity, Cursor, and Airwallex generate hundreds of millions in pipeline. But we kept hearing from customers that the handoff from Growth to Sales was important, but wildly painful.\n\nWe believe that Growth teams and sellers should work together, augmented by AI, to outperform teams 10x their size.\n\n--\nEnter Unify for Sales Reps: a new AI-powered system-of-action, specifically designed to amplify human sellers by automating busywork and surfacing high-intent, actionable leads. \n\nHere are the products that we’re launching:\n\n(1) AI Research Assistant: Instantly synthesizes prospect news, CRM history, and web data into concise, actionable reports, powered by our Observation Model built on OpenAI’s o3. No more context-switching, ever.\n\n(2) Unify Browser Extension: Turn any LinkedIn profile into a fully enriched email or phone number with one click, powered by our market-leading contact data waterfall.\n\n(3) Manual Email, LinkedIn, and Call steps - Layer human-triggered emails, LinkedIn touches, action items, phone calls reminders, and more in multi-step sequences. All this, alongside the automations and managed deliverability Unify is known for.\n\n(4) Tasks Dashboard: A centralized command center for reps to prioritize and execute tasks, and for managers to effortlessly track progress.\n\n--\nUnify is the only platform built to seamlessly serve growth teams and sales reps.\n\nAnd we eat our own dogfood. For our outbound team (Charlie Harry Tarun) 30% of sourced pipeline originates from Unify-powered signals. \n\nA huge shoutout to the team behind this launch: Sam Solomon Noah Young Kunal Ross Aidan Fabian Hyewon Tim Mike\n\nLink to the full launch announcement and demo booking link in comments 👇",
