      "The AI Future is Already Here, it’s Just Not Productized Yet (new post in comments!) \n\nGenAI is slashing the cost of productivity, and presenting opportunities in every sector. Soon, the these tasks will be fully automated by AI.\n\nBUT, while AI is everywhere, the real application level breakthroughs have yet to be built 💡\n\nHere’s a look at what's working today, a framework for AI's immediate business impact, and where new companies can emerge:\n\n1/ Tasks contained to a specific role? AI agents\n2/ Tasks contained to an industry function? AI vertical software\n3/ Tasks spread throughout your workflows? AI horizontal software\n\nIf you have domain expertise about a process, workflow, or role that can be rethought with AI, we’d love to talk to you. If you’re a larger company looking to get started — or just move faster — taking a hard look at where these automatable tasks exist in your organization is a good start.",
