    postContent:
      "On Wednesday, I spoke on a founder-led sales panel in a room full of founders searching for the \"silver bullet\" growth hack.\n\nHow to grow from $0 - $100K ARR.\nHow to grow from $100K - $1M ARR.\n\nBy moving through 3 stages:\n\nStage 1: Message-Market Fit\n\n→ We made 500 cold calls per day (shoutout Max Woo 👋 )\n→ If I couldn't book the meeting on the call, the value prop wasn't strong enough\n→ We made zero revenue from the cold calls\n→ But found message-market fit\n\nStage 2: Trust Building\n\n→ We started hosting intimate events for our ICP\n→ No pitching. No demos. Just connecting people.\n→ This built trust and led to our first customers.\n\nStage 3: Content Focus\n\n→ At this stage, we stopped EVERYTHING else and started posting content\n→ I went from 3K to 21K followers in 6 months.\n→ Now, all our revenue comes from inbound.\n\nThe key insight:\n\nMessage-market fit leads to product-market fit.\n\nMost founders skip straight to building without knowing what resonates with their customers.\n\nYour job in the early days isn’t to scale.\n\nIt’s to learn. Iterate. Adapt.\n\nShout out to Saud Aziz, Stephen Hakami and our host Taylor Del Giudice 🦆",
