      "I'm sick of reading fluffy LinkedIn growth advice. Most of them are lies.\n\nOctober 2023: I started posting consistently with 5K followers.\n\nAt first, engagement was through the roof.\nFriends were hyping every post.\nI thought I cracked the code.\n\nThen reality hit. The algorithm pulled the rug.\n\n→ Engagement dropped 75%.\n→ 100-like posts dropped to 20.\n→ It felt like I was posting into the void.\n\nBut I kept posting. Every. Single. Day.\n\nDecember came, finally, a breakthrough.\nOne post popped. Then another.\nI climbed to 7K followers.\n\nI thought I was back.\n\nThen the holidays came. I got busy with the startup.\n\nTook a \"quick\" two-week break from posting.\n\nCame back in January… and boom:\nEngagement tanked again - down 3X.\nI had to rebuild from scratch. Again.\n\nAnd here’s the part that’ll surprise you:\n\nI’ve been creating viral content for 10+ years.\nMillions of followers across Instagram, YouTube, TikTok.\n\nBut LinkedIn took me six months to figure out.\n\nThere are no shortcuts. There's no hack. There's no \"one weird trick.\"\n\nIt's just showing up when you don't want to. Posting when your engagement sucks. Experimenting when nothing's working.",
