    type: "Image",
    postContent:
      'In 2025, AI notetakers have become a commodity. BUT there are 5 things that still set the best apart:\n\n#𝟭 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝘂𝘁𝗼-𝗽𝗼𝗽𝘂𝗹𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀 𝗖𝗥𝗠 𝗳𝗶𝗲𝗹𝗱𝘀\n\nAdvanced notetakers use prompts to populate/ update CRM fields.\n↳ Improves CRM data hygiene.\n↳ Drives productivity gains\n↳ Reps love it!\n\nHere are details that matter:\n • Which objects can be updated (Opps, Accounts...)\n • Which fields are supported (Amount, Picklists...)\n • Is the prompt library optimized by field type\n • Can admins map fields to AI prompts\n • Can admins adjust AI prompts\n • Are custom objects supported\n\n-\nPS: Get our FREE AI Notetaker tool checklist with 50+ criteria:\n\n1. Like + Comment "Weflow AI Notetaker"\n2. Connect with me on LI\n\n#𝟮 𝗔𝗜 𝗴𝗲𝗻𝗲𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀 𝗺𝗲𝗲𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘀𝘂𝗺𝗺𝗮𝗿𝗶𝗲𝘀\n\nAdvanced notetakers generate meeting summaries to\n↳ automate note-taking processes\n↳ store in CRM\n\nDetails that matter:\n • Can you create custom AI summary templates?\n • Can you combine multiple prompts/templates?\n • Can you assign templates to user profiles?\n • Are summaries logged to CRM event objects?\n • Is there a comprehensive prompt library?\n\n#𝟯 𝗔𝗜 𝘄𝗿𝗶𝘁𝗲𝘀 𝗳𝗼𝗹𝗹𝗼𝘄-𝘂𝗽 𝗲𝗺𝗮𝗶𝗹\n\nAdvanced notetakers compose follow-up emails for\n↳ faster & more effective follow-ups\n↳ better rep productivity\n↳ higher deal velocity\n\nDetails that matter:\n • Can you create email templates self-service?\n • Can you assign templates to user profiles?\n • Can you customize the email prompts?\n • Are emails formatted to copy-paste?\n\n#𝟰 𝗔𝘂𝘁𝗼-𝗰𝗮𝗽𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗲 𝗲𝗺𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘀, 𝗺𝗲𝗲𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴𝘀 & 𝗰𝗼𝗻𝘁𝗮𝗰𝘁𝘀\n\nAdvanced notetakers offer automated activity capture\n\n↳ to capture email, meetings, contacts\n↳ for better reporting on activities\n↳ to avoid duplication of events\n\nHere are details that matter:\n • Is there a central app to get permission to email & calendar events?\n • Can you capture meetings if not recorded?\n • Can you capture emails (incoming, outgoing)?\n • Can you capture contacts that are not in the CRM?\n • Are activities auto-mapped to right records?\n • Are there manual controls in Outlook/ Google?\n\n#𝟱 𝗔𝗜 𝗽𝗿𝗼𝘃𝗶𝗱𝗲𝘀 𝗮𝗱𝘃𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲𝗱 𝗱𝗲𝗮𝗹 𝗶𝗻𝘀𝗶𝗴𝗵𝘁𝘀\n\nTop notetakers turn conversations into insights to\n↳ provide deal signals, warnings, and scores\n↳ enable reps/ managers to spot risks\n↳ improve deal execution\n\nHere are details that matter:\n • What signals exist (stalling, push count...)?\n • Can you easily create deal boards?\n • Can you configure warnings?\n • Do you see activity velocity?\n • Is there a deal score?\n\nWhat would you add? Comment 👇\n\n___\n\nPS: Weflow\'s Conversation Intelligence does all of this by default. \n\nDM me to learn more or go to getweflow(.)com\n\n#revops #ai #gtm',
